title: 'Good but sizing issue'
body: Tshirt quality is superb at such low price but there are some serious sizing issues with this brand. I bought Pomegranate colour tshirt in M size and it fits perfectly to me so bought more colours. But other coloured tshirt don't fit perfectly to me. They are just too loose and long. Also tried size S but it's just too tight. It's frustrating. Please fix your sizing issue.
